<function>

access:   public

name: buildSelect

param: array, $parts

return: void

</function>

Adds a LIMIT clause (or equivalent) to a SELECT statement.

* Parameters:

 * array //$parts//: The SELECT statement parts.

* Returns void

Still not great, but much more efficient than old way.
